title: Blueorange Coffee and Bagel - Alserbachstrasse
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Catering, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe with free Wi-Fi. Has marked vegan choices in hot and cold bagels, sandwiches, wraps, lunch specials. Free Wi-Fi. Organic fair trade coffee, tea, muesli and shakes with soy milk. Vegan cheese available. Located in the 9th district. Selection of newspapers, magazines and books for guests.
